# ipasub rules
ipasub,ɔ ERASE,,7,,,"removes the inherent vowel when there's a diacritic after",
ipasub,e ERASE i,ɔ i,7,,,"vowel clean-up: diacritic for this vowel sequence is technically two diacritics",
