ipasub,({Nvowels}) NASAL, \1̃,6,,,"chandrabindu makes previous vowel nasal",
ipasub,NASAL,,2,,,"the nasalization diacritic may follow consonants, however, nasal consonants are not contrastive, so the nasalization diacritic will be removed",
